{\"ngram\": \"a meet\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1382}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the rigours of seven events in the heptathlon are a different matter, but she said: \\\"I think I am in good shape.\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1531, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the rigours\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1430}, {\"ngram\": \"seven events\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1446}, {\"ngram\": \"the heptathlon\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1464}, {\"ngram\": \"a different matter\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1487}, {\"ngram\": \"good shape\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1530}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All the signs are there that I am coming into shape.\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All the signs\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1545}, {\"ngram\": \"shape\", \"from\": 1578, \"to\": 1583}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's all I can ask for.\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1610, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am just praying I can take that into the heptathlon.\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1667, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the heptathlon\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1666}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was really happy with being able to get into the 6.50s [in the long jump] straight away, because it was an event I had not done since Budapest.\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1813, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1804, \"end\": 1812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9998647319030544, \"rank\": 0.00013528639691441646, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 6.50s\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1724}, {\"ngram\": \"the long jump\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1742}, {\"ngram\": \"an event\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Tendinitis is an ongoing thing.\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1847, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tendinitis\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 1826}, {\"ngram\": \"an ongoing thing\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1846}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think a lot of people struggle with it.\", \"from\": 1848, \"to\": 1889, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1861}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1865, \"to\": 1871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It comes and goes, it gets bad and good again, so it's something I have to keep an eye on, but it's something I have got on top of now.\", \"from\": 1890, \"to\": 2025, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1954}, {\"ngram\": \"an eye\", \"from\": 1970, \"to\": 1976}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 1999}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2017}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But you cannot predict a heptathlon.\\\"\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2063, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a heptathlon\", \"from\": 2049, \"to\": 2061}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Question marks will remain about Johnson-Thompson's ability to go for multi-event gold, in contrast to Hodgkinson and Hudson-Smith, who have marked themselves as golden favourites in the 800m and 400m respectively.\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2279, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2168, \"end\": 2178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.985456526418413, \"rank\": 0.014758107731705243, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Question marks\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2079}, {\"ngram\": \"Johnson-Thompson's ability\", \"from\": 2098, \"to\": 2124}, {\"ngram\": \"multi-event gold\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2151}, {\"ngram\": \"contrast\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2164}, {\"ngram\": \"Hudson-Smith\", \"from\": 2183,